{"tid":2345464,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"北京健康寶洩露個人資料   過千明星藝人身份證號碼遭賤賣","createTime":"2020-12-29T13:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T16:29:38.000Z","uid":66271,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b89cb8baeef1b110246e90f99e7574a6b4c2aed8","tid":2345464,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1229-4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F1229-4a.jpg&h=4afc03f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了武漢肺炎防疫而設的「北京健康寶」程式，日前爆出嚴重私隱問題，這個基於微信小程序的防控數據系統，被爆洩露大量用戶個人資料，結果有大量明星藝人，包括楊冪、王俊凱、易烊千璽等的健康寶照片、身份證號碼和相關的核酸檢測信息被放上網賤價販賣。<br />\n<br />\n偶像「TNT 時代少年團」7 人的健康寶照片被人以 3 人民幣打包出售，另外亦有 70 多名藝人的健康寶照片以 2 人民幣被打包出售，更誇張是超過 1,000 名藝人的身份證號碼以 1 人民幣發售。上述明星藝人個人資料買賣在網上群組首先出現，只要在「北京健康寶」註冊，再輸入明星姓名和身份證號碼，毋須進行面部識別，就能夠獲得相關明星的健康寶照片、武肺檢測日期、機構和測試結果。<br />\n<br />\n中國傳媒報導證實，部份外洩的明星資料屬實，而負責研發「北京健康寶」的北京中關村科學城城市大腦公司表示，正在跟進今次資料外洩事件。有中國律師指透過出售他人個人資料謀利，或在未經對方同意情況下公開其個人資料，例如健康寶照片和身份證號碼，這些行為都構成侵犯公民個人信息與肖像權，屬於違法行為。"},{"pid":"c16dc7e7a148c82fe98fbebcce4b568b5d56699e","tid":2345464,"uid":224533,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"支國自古以來都不需要私隱"},{"pid":"f32f023f2de22485ef8fe9d0164f2579547321ca","tid":2345464,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"金？？"},{"pid":"fde89166611941aa3baa9c97d89ad421a12eabd3","tid":2345464,"uid":117301,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"中國人有需要私隱嗎？"},{"pid":"00926a5a306371bf5334b1ecd3f707cfb0055d37","tid":2345464,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"乜寶物寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff98ce40a7a685e03191e7f2b0f0422125693f0","tid":2345464,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"實係美國佬搞事"},{"pid":"3db976474b5f6c38c27215fea23e25f704898828","tid":2345464,"uid":356101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fde89166611941aa3baa9c97d89ad421a12eabd3","tid":2345464,"uid":117301,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"中國人有需要私隱嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"私隱值唔值錢先?<br />\n值錢? 咁我賣你d資料賺錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係大陸有錢賺,老母都賣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76abee909d85bc5ab6f545dca4b4ab55dbb71a23","tid":2345464,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人講私隱 笑話"},{"pid":"42f47a33f8dad414c5694b34fc0d1308b0a5ae9b","tid":2345464,"uid":146267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行得正企得正要咩私隱？"},{"pid":"f7ccf0c88ccbb0985fdb58d578fc02806d38bd97","tid":2345464,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"支那人有私隱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條命都係黨嘅"},{"pid":"5dd38390dde5c071dce970e107111d429e8c4061","tid":2345464,"uid":155682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"身份證號碼呢啲政府又有，銀行又有，電訊公司又有，好多公私營機構都有，私咩隱啫，尤佢囉！"},{"pid":"d38d6993b0f5134909efe6d33cdf694938beae94","tid":2345464,"uid":316927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"正呀 全部參軍"},{"pid":"c59cfc092a532cc271fec89a76d368444070a926","tid":2345464,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42f47a33f8dad414c5694b34fc0d1308b0a5ae9b","tid":2345464,"uid":146267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202